strings: <voice_0x010016BF><se_low>Yangus: Heh heh, long time no see, eh!? I ain't seen your mug since we polished off that fat geezer!
<voice_0x010016C6><se_low>Yangus: I'm well chuffed I can 'elp you out on yer first big job, an' all!

<voice_0x010016C7><se_low>Yangus: An' it's for none other than our darlin' 'orse-prin<endash> Oh! Listen to me!
She ain't an 'orse any more, is she!?
<voice_0x010016C8><se_low>Yangus: So we're escortin' the Princess to 'er weddin' at Savella Cathedral, right?

<voice_0x010016C9><se_low>Yangus: I dunno, though.
Beats me why she's still marryin' that Charmless bloke after all that's 'appened.

<voice_0x010016CA><se_low>Yangus: Oh yeah! Nearly forgot!
I was s'posed to give you a message from this old minister I saw on the way over.

<voice_0x010016CB><se_low>Yangus: Seems the Princess is ready to deport now,
so ya can go an' fetch 'er from 'er room, like.

<voice_0x010016CC><se_low>Yangus: I'll be waitin' down in the courtyard then, eh?
See you in a bit.
<voice_0x010016C0><se_high>Red: Yeah, we ain't 'eard a flamin' peep from you since. I mean, I know yer the strong silent type, but still...
<voice_0x010016C1><se_high>Red: I've 'ad to put up wiv this one grumblin' and moanin' the whole time.

<voice_0x010016C2><se_high>Red: Honest to Goddess, 'is first words to me
when 'e come to me gaff were,
‘D'you think the guv's forgot about me?’
<voice_0x010016C3><se_low>Yangus: Awright, Red, there's no need to make me sound so flamin' soft!
<voice_0x010016C4><se_high>Red: Wot? I'm only tellin' the truth.

<voice_0x010016C5><se_low>Yangus: Er...any-anyway, guv, I 'eard the news.
Head guard, eh? It don't get much better
than that, does it!? You deserve it, though.
